1
00:00:05,397 --> 00:00:07,460
Murakaza neza na none muri 5.3.

2
00:00:08,252 --> 00:00:13,389
Uyu munsi turaza kuganira
kubijyanye n'amategeko birebana no kwihangira imirimo

3
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:17,269
Hanyuma tunyure twihuse

4
00:00:17,269 --> 00:00:20,701
muri bimwe mubintu byo kurwego rwo hejuru
ugomba kuba uri gutekerezaho

5
00:00:20,701 --> 00:00:23,056
aka kanya, mugihe uri gutekereza
kugutangiza kampani nshyashya,

6
00:00:24,567 --> 00:00:26,193
Icyintu ngarukaho nanone ni uko

7
00:00:26,194 --> 00:00:29,130
ibi mutagomba kubifata
nk'ubujyanama mubyerekeye amategeko! (agatwenge)

8
00:00:29,322 --> 00:00:31,739
Rero sinabaha ubjyana muby'amategeko,

9
00:00:31,740 --> 00:00:33,709
Jye ndi kubaha amakuru
hano

10
00:00:33,709 --> 00:00:35,020
mushobora gusanga ashimishije,

11
00:00:35,020 --> 00:00:39,439
Hanyuma ukaba wavugana n'umunyamategeko
ubaye ufite ibibazo bifite aho bihuriye nabyo.

12
00:00:39,630 --> 00:00:42,105
Turaza kuvuga kubyo "usabwa"

13
00:00:42,548 --> 00:00:44,944
Turavuga gacye ku "gutandukanya kampnai na nyirayo"

14
00:00:45,617 --> 00:00:48,086
gutanga imigabane, bishatse kuvuga iki.

15
00:00:48,604 --> 00:00:51,414
Turaza kuvuga 
"k'umutungo mu by'ubwenge"

16
00:00:51,414 --> 00:00:53,102
hanze y'igihugu cyawe,

17
00:00:54,325 --> 00:00:57,638
amasezerano yo kudahangana niki,

18
00:00:58,571 --> 00:01:01,302
Ni gute ukora kubintu
bijyanye n'ibyo gicuruzwa gishobora kwangiza, ese ni iki

19
00:01:01,676 --> 00:01:04,190
Hanyuma, turanabaha ibitekerezo

20
00:01:04,190 --> 00:01:06,432
ku kuntu wabona umunyamategeko.

21
00:01:06,825 --> 00:01:10,933
Reka rero dutangire
aka kanya tureba kumadeni.

22
00:01:11,432 --> 00:01:13,179
Ideni ni iki?

23
00:01:13,838 --> 00:01:18,049
Ideni ni igihe ufite inshingano

24
00:01:18,049 --> 00:01:20,450
kukintu runaka wakoze.

25
00:01:20,882 --> 00:01:26,023
Bisa n'ibivuggitse nabi
kuberako ari bibi.

26
00:01:26,023 --> 00:01:29,092
Haba hari icyintu cyibi
cyabaye cyangwa cyiri kuba rero,

27
00:01:29,092 --> 00:01:32,259
Abantu bari gushaka nkuko tubivuga
"gushaka ufite icyaha",

28
00:01:32,704 --> 00:01:36,695
baka gerageza kubona umuntu ugomba kubibazwa,
muburyo bujyanye n'iby'amategeko.

29
00:01:36,695 --> 00:01:39,312
Rero, Kwishyuzwa
ni igihe ari wowe ugomba kubazwa

30
00:01:39,312 --> 00:01:41,065
icyintu cyibi runaka cyabaye.

31
00:01:42,628 --> 00:01:44,124
Nka rwiyemezamirimo,

32
00:01:44,125 --> 00:01:46,651
Hari impamvu nyinshi
ugomba kujyira byinshi ubazwa;

33
00:01:46,651 --> 00:01:50,022
Turaza kuvuga kuri
bimwe muri byo by'ingenzi uyu munsi.

34
00:01:51,602 --> 00:01:53,268
Murugendo rwo gushyira mubikorwa umushinga wawe

35
00:01:53,268 --> 00:01:54,957
ushobora kuba warijyeze gufata
icyemezo cyibi cyijyanye n'umushinga

36
00:01:54,957 --> 00:01:57,938
Cyakomerekeje umuntu
mubijyanye n'amafaranga cyagwa ibindi.

37
00:01:58,798 --> 00:02:02,472
Ushobora kuba uri gukorera
muburyo bwa forode

38
00:02:02,472 --> 00:02:05,035
hari amakuru runaka uri guhisha
cyangwa uri kubeshya, n'ibindi.

39
00:02:05,614 --> 00:02:10,557
Kwirengajyiza, bibaho iyo uri
kwirengajyiza icyintu runaka

40
00:02:10,557 --> 00:02:14,927
uziko ari cyibi cyangwa cyagira ibyo cyangiza.

41
00:02:15,671 --> 00:02:18,891
Hashobora kuba hari n'ibiza bijyanye n'abakozi
cyangwa ibibazo bijyanye n'ibiro bibashinzwe

42
00:02:18,891 --> 00:02:21,964
ushobora kuba ushinzwa
cyangwa bwa nyuma bikaba,

43
00:02:21,964 --> 00:02:24,767
Ibicuruzwa byagira umuntu byangiriza,

44
00:02:24,959 --> 00:02:28,823
--ari mubintu bigaragara,
ari ubw'amafaranga--

45
00:02:29,025 --> 00:02:33,673
nabyo ukaba washobora 
kubibazwa.

46
00:02:33,673 --> 00:02:37,297
Reka rero tuganire kuri uru rutonde rubi hano,

47
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:43,762
kandi tujyerageze kumva ibibazo
bya buri kimwe muri byo.

48
00:02:44,959 --> 00:02:49,330
Twavuze kubijyanye
no gutandukanya kampani na nyirayo mugace ka 4,

49
00:02:49,562 --> 00:02:53,698
ariko nashakaga kubaha
ubusobanuro burambuyeho gato nanone

50
00:02:53,953 --> 00:02:55,877
iyo tuvuze ku ideni,

51
00:02:55,994 --> 00:02:58,780
ufite amadeni yo ku giti cyawe.

52
00:02:59,394 --> 00:03:03,798
Hanyuma, bijyendeye,
kuburyo kampani yawe yandikishijwe,

53
00:03:04,507 --> 00:03:06,623
ushobora kujyira amadeni,
ya kampani yose.

54
00:03:07,295 --> 00:03:09,417
Rero biterwa n'igihugu,

55
00:03:10,406 --> 00:03:13,509
Ariko ibihugu byose biratandukana

56
00:03:14,013 --> 00:03:17,350
hagati y'ibintu
bifite amadeni atajyira aho agarukira

57
00:03:17,962 --> 00:03:21,845
n'ubundi buryo bw'amafaranga 
ajyira aho agarukira

58
00:03:22,619 --> 00:03:26,295
Rero, akenshi iyo uri
nyiri iyo kampani wenyine

59
00:03:26,624 --> 00:03:29,036
Ibyo tuzabyita ko kompani ari iy'umuntu umwe

60
00:03:29,419 --> 00:03:31,865
uwo n'ubundi akaba ari umutungo wawe;

61
00:03:31,865 --> 00:03:34,235
uri muri rusange
kwinjiza amafaranga kuruhande,

62
00:03:34,429 --> 00:03:37,733
ndetse ufite n'uburyo buto ukoramo.

63
00:03:38,004 --> 00:03:43,367
Hanyuma rero, kubwamahirwe macye
amadeni yawe aba atagira aho agarukira.

64
00:03:43,367 --> 00:03:46,256
Rero, iyo hajyize icyiba kuri kampani

65
00:03:46,256 --> 00:03:48,144
hakajyira ikijyenda nabi muri kampani,

66
00:03:48,144 --> 00:03:50,134
ubwo uba uri mubyago

67
00:03:50,273 --> 00:03:52,643
byo kwishyura ibyangijwe,
wateje,

68
00:03:52,643 --> 00:03:55,522
Ibyangiritse muburyo bw'amafaranga
cyangwa muburyo bw'ibintu bifatika,

69
00:03:55,522 --> 00:03:57,619
biturutse kumitungo yawe bwite.

70
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:03,714
Akenshi, kompani y'umuntu kujyiticye,
bikunda gukorwa muntangiriro,

71
00:04:03,714 --> 00:04:06,294
cyangwa kubwoko bwa kampani budafite ingaruka zigaragara.

72
00:04:06,294 --> 00:04:08,459
Ufite kampani yo kujyira abantu inama,

73
00:04:09,119 --> 00:04:11,329
ntabakiriya benshi ufite,

74
00:04:11,902 --> 00:04:14,838
Ariko ntacyo bitwaye kuko ukora ibintu byawe

75
00:04:14,838 --> 00:04:17,561
hari amahirwe macye
ko wafatanya n'undi muntu

76
00:04:17,561 --> 00:04:21,565
bityo rero nta bwoba ufite
kubijyanye n'imitungo yawe.

77
00:04:22,353 --> 00:04:25,390
Ubufatanye bw'abantu rero nabyo birasa, muburyo bwishi;

78
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:27,919
ubu ibihugu bynshi bitandukanye bifite
amategeko ajyenga ubufatanye bw'abantu,

79
00:04:27,919 --> 00:04:30,308
ariko ubwoko bworoheje bw'ubufatanye ni

80
00:04:30,308 --> 00:04:33,453
aho utangirana ishoramari n'umuntu mufatanyije,

81
00:04:33,742 --> 00:04:36,587
hanyuma bitewe n'uburyo mufatanya

82
00:04:36,587 --> 00:04:37,840
ndetse n'igihugu,

83
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,313
ariko akenshi,

84
00:04:39,313 --> 00:04:44,236
Abafatanyabikorwa baba barebwa,
n'amadeni yose uri uwo mushinga.

85
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:47,405
Cyanga se niba hari abafatanyabikorwa benshi
bose biba bibareba,

86
00:04:47,405 --> 00:04:49,361
Hari n'amako amwe
y'ubufatanye

87
00:04:49,361 --> 00:04:55,624
Aho abafatanya bikorwa atari bose baba barebwa n'amadeni,
abafatanya bikorwa muburyo bworoheje, abafite aho bagarukira, n'ibindi.

88
00:04:56,963 --> 00:05:02,839
Ariko muri rusange, iyo abafatanya bikorwa
bishize hamwe mubufatanye

89
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:07,851
kandi bakaba bahujwe kandi barebwa

90
00:05:07,851 --> 00:05:09,971
nikintu icyo aricyo cyose cyaba kuri kampani.

91
00:05:09,971 --> 00:05:11,467
Rero ubufataye,  muri rusange,

92
00:05:11,467 --> 00:05:14,177
ntago ikurinda 
kubibazo bijyanye n'amadeni

93
00:05:15,375 --> 00:05:17,849
Hanyuma kandi habaho n'amako atandukanye
y'ibyo abantu bita

94
00:05:17,849 --> 00:05:19,661
kampni z'amadeni ajyira aho agarukira,

95
00:05:19,661 --> 00:05:22,929
Kandi ayo makampani akajyira
amazina atandukanye mubihugu bitandukanye,

96
00:05:22,929 --> 00:05:25,104
ariko ihame ry'ingenzi ni

97
00:05:25,104 --> 00:05:29,002
wenda mushobora kuba mufite
umushnga w'abantu kugiti cyabo,

98
00:05:29,002 --> 00:05:31,605
bisobanuye ko,
abanyamigabane aba ari abantu bacye

99
00:05:31,605 --> 00:05:34,800
--ibyo twabivuzeho gato,
igihe twavugaga kubijyanye no gukusanya igishoro--

100
00:05:36,257 --> 00:05:39,339
cyagwa mukajyira umushinga wa rusange,

101
00:05:39,734 --> 00:05:44,044
ibyo bikaba ari uko abanyamigabane 
benshi cyane rwose,

102
00:05:44,044 --> 00:05:47,899
kandi iyo muri gukora
amahame n'ingingo

103
00:05:47,899 --> 00:05:49,819
z'uburyo imishinga yanyu ikorwa,

104
00:05:49,948 --> 00:05:53,129
hanyuma mukemerera 
abantu bose kwinjira mo

105
00:05:53,129 --> 00:05:54,994
agura imigabane muri kampani yanyu.

106
00:05:55,852 --> 00:05:57,993
Ayo moko yose se ahuriye kuki?

107
00:05:57,993 --> 00:06:02,665
Bitandukanira kukuba bimwe byoroshye binatwra amafranga macye
ibindi bikurinda gukorwaho n'amadeni.

108
00:06:02,665 --> 00:06:08,526
Rero, kampani y'umuntu ku giti cye, iroroshye cyane,
ushobora kuyikora ako kanya,

109
00:06:08,526 --> 00:06:09,836
mubihugu byinshi ku isi

110
00:06:09,836 --> 00:06:12,890
kurundi ruhande ntago,
ikurinda kukuba wahangana n'ibintu by'amadeni.

111
00:06:12,890 --> 00:06:17,388
Hanyuma kandi, uko ujyenda wejyera
kampani y'amadeni afite aho agarukira,

112
00:06:17,691 --> 00:06:20,620
Biba bigoye kuko
uba ugomba 

113
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:23,027
kunyura muntambwe nyinshi
mu kwandikisha kampani n'ibindi.

114
00:06:23,027 --> 00:06:24,389
gusa ku rundi ruhande,

115
00:06:24,389 --> 00:06:26,982
ariko kurundi ruhande ibyo bikurinda
kuruhande rujyanye n'ibintu by'amadeni.

116
00:06:26,982 --> 00:06:28,693
Rero, ni ikintu cyo gutekerezaho,

117
00:06:28,693 --> 00:06:30,878
Uko ushaka guteganya iterambere ryawe

118
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:36,585
uko ujyenda wegera kugukora
no gucuruza igicuruzwa cyawe.

119
00:06:39,992 --> 00:06:44,614
Ntibiikurinda;
ntnakimwe muri ubwo bwoko twavuze haruguru

120
00:06:44,614 --> 00:06:46,801
kukijyanye na forode no kutita kubintu.

121
00:06:47,732 --> 00:06:51,717
Si uko uteganya
gukora forode cyangwa kutita kubintu.

122
00:06:52,234 --> 00:06:54,441
Ibi nabyo turabivugaho muminota micye,

123
00:06:54,441 --> 00:06:56,414
Ariko niba hari amakuru uzi 
kucyintu cyiri kuba

124
00:06:56,414 --> 00:06:57,814
ugomba kujyira icyo ukora byihuse.

125
00:06:57,814 --> 00:07:01,466
Ntugomba kujyerageza guhishira ibintu
cyangwa guhisha ibibazo, n'ibindi.

126
00:07:01,466 --> 00:07:05,048
cyane cyane ibibazo bishobora 
gutera ibintu kwangirika kuruhande rw'abakiriya, n'ibindi.

127
00:07:05,768 --> 00:07:08,788
Mubihe nk'ibyo ibihugu byinshi

128
00:07:09,244 --> 00:07:11,757
ushobora gufatwa nk'urebwa

129
00:07:12,479 --> 00:07:15,628
n'ibibazo byatewe, n'ibikorwa byawe by'amanyanga

130
00:07:16,146 --> 00:07:19,934
n'ubwo mwaba muffite
kampani y'amadeni afite aho agarukira.

131
00:07:19,934 --> 00:07:26,513
Rero, witonde hano
icyo ibi bikurinda ni

132
00:07:26,514 --> 00:07:28,661
ibyemezo bibi byo mumushinga.

133
00:07:28,662 --> 00:07:31,166
Muri rusange, mubuhugu byinshi,

134
00:07:31,323 --> 00:07:32,835
ntago wabazwa

135
00:07:32,835 --> 00:07:34,733
ibintu kuko wafashe ibyemezo bibi bijyanye n'ishoramari

136
00:07:35,054 --> 00:07:37,351
Sawa, reka rero tuvuge kubijyanye n'akazi noneho.

137
00:07:39,951 --> 00:07:42,203
Ibibazo bijyanye n'akazi ni ukuvuga

138
00:07:42,203 --> 00:07:43,862
ibijyane n'amasezerano mujyirana

139
00:07:43,862 --> 00:07:47,337
n'abashinze kampani
ndetse n'abakozi banyu.

140
00:07:48,023 --> 00:07:50,840
Rero icyo nsa n'ubajyiraho inama hano

141
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:53,751
Mubihe by'intangiriro,

142
00:07:53,751 --> 00:07:56,843
Ndavuga, igihe utekereza ko wakora kampani

143
00:07:57,032 --> 00:07:59,988
kandi ukumva ushobora kuzakorana
n'abantu runaka,

144
00:08:00,335 --> 00:08:03,445
ushobora kukora 
nk'amasezerano y'agateganyo.

145
00:08:04,341 --> 00:08:08,899
Ukayakora hari abantu bose
barebwa n'uwo mushinga

146
00:08:08,899 --> 00:08:10,362
muntangiriro.

147
00:08:10,981 --> 00:08:12,612
Kand ugomba gushaka inzira

148
00:08:12,701 --> 00:08:17,295
yo kubishyura cyangwa kubahemba,

149
00:08:17,549 --> 00:08:19,245
hanyuma nabo bakavuga ko babyemeye,

150
00:08:19,526 --> 00:08:21,389
kujyirango mwirinde kutazahuza mubihe bizaza.

151
00:08:21,389 --> 00:08:23,550
mugasa n'abakora 
inkuru ya kampani

152
00:08:23,550 --> 00:08:25,948
abitabiriye, abajyize uruhare,

153
00:08:25,948 --> 00:08:27,770
ndetse n'icyo bagomba kungukiramo.

154
00:08:27,770 --> 00:08:29,576
Ibi birinda iki?

155
00:08:29,576 --> 00:08:32,510
Ibi birinda ibihe byo kutamenya abashinze ibintu

156
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:34,533
Aho umuntu aba yari 
ahari muntangiriro

157
00:08:34,533 --> 00:08:36,404
hanyuma bakabura,

158
00:08:36,404 --> 00:08:38,532
hanyuma, kampani yakunguka cyane,

159
00:08:38,532 --> 00:08:40,636
bakongera abakaboneka bakavuga bati
"nijye 

160
00:08:40,636 --> 00:08:42,101
watekereje kuri ibi bintu byose,

161
00:08:42,101 --> 00:08:44,142
cyari igitekerezo cyanjye muntangiriro,

162
00:08:44,142 --> 00:08:46,152
ndashaka ko munyishyura.." n'ibindi n'ibindi.

163
00:08:46,152 --> 00:08:49,207
Aho mugahura n'ibibazo by'abantu
baza mutazi iyo bava

164
00:08:49,207 --> 00:08:51,056
kampani yanyu yaramaze kumera neza.

165
00:08:51,953 --> 00:08:55,922
Ubu bwoko bw'amasezerano ya hakiri kare

166
00:08:55,923 --> 00:08:57,999
ni na meza mugihe cyo gutegura imisoro

167
00:08:57,999 --> 00:09:00,749
mugihe uwo mushinga
waba utangiye

168
00:09:00,749 --> 00:09:03,794
mukazaba mwaratekereje neza

169
00:09:03,794 --> 00:09:05,621
ahari kubijyanye n'imisoro,

170
00:09:05,621 --> 00:09:07,225
kuko haba hari imisoro

171
00:09:07,225 --> 00:09:12,187
y'ijyihe winjije amafaranga
cyangwa ibihembo runaka wabonye.

172
00:09:14,122 --> 00:09:16,018
Reka tuvuge kukintu cyijyane n'ububasha nk'umunota.

173
00:09:16,846 --> 00:09:19,255
Imigabanr y'abatangije umushinga
n'abakozi batangiranye nawo,

174
00:09:19,693 --> 00:09:22,635
haba ari ububasha bajyiye bafite uko ibihe bjyenda.

175
00:09:22,655 --> 00:09:25,718
icyo mudashaka gukora ni amasezerano
aho muntangiriro

176
00:09:26,587 --> 00:09:28,314
umuntu wese afite ibintu byinshi,

177
00:09:28,314 --> 00:09:33,464
hanyuma umuntu umwe akavamo
ndetse uyu uvuyemo,

178
00:09:33,727 --> 00:09:37,422
akaba yari afite imigabane myinshi muri kampani
mwamuhaye muntangiriro.

179
00:09:37,561 --> 00:09:40,472
Hagomba kuba igihembo 
cy'uko mugumye muri kampani

180
00:09:40,473 --> 00:09:43,089
ari cyo kubona imigabane myinshi.

181
00:09:43,127 --> 00:09:46,215
Icyibaho ni uko akenshi
haba hari imigabane imwe

182
00:09:46,215 --> 00:09:48,026
ihabwa abashinze kampani,

183
00:09:48,530 --> 00:09:54,139
hanyuma iyo migabane ikayira agaciro ari uko mujyeze ahantu runaka,

184
00:09:54,570 --> 00:09:58,076
haba icyiciro y'umushinga
cyangwa igihe runaka,

185
00:09:58,076 --> 00:10:01,351
kujyira bibe igihembo cy'abantu bagumye 
mumushinga igihe cyirekire bakanakora akazi kenshi.

186
00:10:01,351 --> 00:10:04,252
Bikarangira bafite uruhande runini rw'umushinga
ndetse ari nabo bayoboye kampani.

187
00:10:04,252 --> 00:10:06,798
Kani ibi bigakorerwa no kubakozi 
batangiranye n'umushinga,

188
00:10:06,798 --> 00:10:10,073
rero ugomba kumenya icyo bakora aho ngaho,

189
00:10:10,073 --> 00:10:12,282
mukamenya neza icyo mugomba kubishyura,

190
00:10:12,282 --> 00:10:16,433
yaba ari amafaranga
imigabane cyangwa imitungo ya kampani.

