00:20:13,401 --> 00:20:18,097
gucibwa amafaranga ya forode cyangwa kutitakubintu,

387
00:20:18,097 --> 00:20:19,660
kuko hari amakuru wari ufite kukintu

388
00:20:19,660 --> 00:20:21,101
hanyuma ntujyire icyo ukora

389
00:20:21,101 --> 00:20:23,257
Numva inkuru nk'izi kenshi 
mumakuru,

390
00:20:23,257 --> 00:20:25,411
ariko ntibiba byumvikana.

391
00:20:25,604 --> 00:20:28,801
Ntukirengajyize ibibazo
iyo ubimenye.

392
00:20:28,801 --> 00:20:30,449
kuko uko ubyirengajyiza,

393
00:20:30,449 --> 00:20:31,824
hakajyira umuntu uvuga ati "a-ha!

394
00:20:31,824 --> 00:20:34,961
ntiwitaye kuri iki kibazo.

395
00:20:34,961 --> 00:20:37,629
ibi wari ubizi
ntiwajyira uwo ubibwiraho

396
00:20:37,629 --> 00:20:39,879
hanyuma abantu 10 barapfa
bitewe na blah, blah, blah.

397
00:20:39,879 --> 00:20:44,694
Rero, ntukirengajyize ibibazo
ijyihe ubimenye

398
00:20:45,081 --> 00:20:47,437
Jya wongera uhamagaze ibicuruzwa, 
ijyisubizo cyoroshye

399
00:20:47,437 --> 00:20:49,821
ni ugukemura ibibazo ukiri gutegura ibicuruzwa.

400
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:53,409
hanyuma nanone byoroshye ho gato 
kubikosora bari gukora ibicuruzwa

401
00:20:54,616 --> 00:20:57,640
bikabona gusohoka bikajya ku isoko

402
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,472
hanyuma rero bitewe n'uruganda,

403
00:20:59,472 --> 00:21:01,889
ugakora amajyerageza,
ukamenya ibintu bimwe bishya, n'ibindi.

404
00:21:03,452 --> 00:21:05,531
ijyihe ibintu byagiye hanze kigacuruzwa

405
00:21:05,531 --> 00:21:08,672
guhamagaza ibintu bikagaruka muri kampani
nicyo gisubizo gihenze cyane.

406
00:21:09,318 --> 00:21:11,435
Nyuma y'ibyo icyibi cyane ni

407
00:21:11,435 --> 00:21:14,541
kuregwa, mugacibwa amafaranga
kubera forode no kutita kubintu,

408
00:21:14,541 --> 00:21:16,211
kuko mwari muzi ikibazo cyera kose

409
00:21:16,211 --> 00:21:17,943
hanyuma mufata umwanzuro wo kutajyira icyo mugikoraho

410
00:21:17,943 --> 00:21:19,875
kuko byari gutwara amafaranga menshi kubikemura.

411
00:21:19,875 --> 00:21:21,102
Aho muhitondere,

412
00:21:21,102 --> 00:21:23,330
kandi mukore kuburyyo musobanukirwa
ibintu bisa n'ibyo.

413
00:21:24,158 --> 00:21:26,917
Nizereko ntabateye ubwoba

414
00:21:26,917 --> 00:21:30,249
kukuba mwakora.. (aseka)
...kumishinga yanyu igitangira!

415
00:21:30,518 --> 00:21:31,959
kuko mugukora kumishinga yanyu igitangira

416
00:21:31,959 --> 00:21:34,652
nicyo cyintu cy'ingenzi kandi gishimishije
muri ibi bintu byose,

417
00:21:34,652 --> 00:21:37,972
kandi ni ukuri ko hari
ibintu byinshi bijyanye n'amategeko hano

418
00:21:37,972 --> 00:21:40,045
bishobora kuba bidashimishije cyane.

419
00:21:40,407 --> 00:21:43,235
Rero akenshi, icyiza

420
00:21:43,235 --> 00:21:46,439
ni ugushaka umujyanama muby'amategeko.

421
00:21:46,439 --> 00:21:48,319
kandi nawe ugomba kumubona.

422
00:21:48,505 --> 00:21:50,718
icyo nakoze hano ni
nabahaye urutonde ruto

423
00:21:50,718 --> 00:21:52,215
rw'ibintu mushobora gutekerezaho

424
00:21:52,215 --> 00:21:55,134
iyo urimo ushaka umujyanama muby'amategeko.

425
00:21:56,243 --> 00:22:00,502
icyintu cya mbere, ese uyu muntu yaba afite uburambe
mubijyanye na kampani zigitangira?

426
00:22:00,502 --> 00:22:01,896
Ibi ni ingirakamaro cyane.

427
00:22:01,896 --> 00:22:04,770
Ntukenye umuntu,
inshuti y'inshuti;

428
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:09,153
"Oh, yego, nakoze utuntu ducye,
nagutunganyiriza ibiyanye na kampani yawe."

429
00:22:09,153 --> 00:22:11,644
aho hantu rero harakomeye

430
00:22:11,644 --> 00:22:14,080
Kuko ukeneye gukorana
n'umuntu

431
00:22:14,174 --> 00:22:17,726
ufite uburambe mugukorana
nama kampani mato

432
00:22:18,579 --> 00:22:21,603
by'akarusho, umuntu ufite uburambe

433
00:22:21,603 --> 00:22:24,815
mucyiciro runaka
uri gukoreramo.

434
00:22:25,058 --> 00:22:27,911
Rero niba uri gukora ibintu bijyanye na mudasobwa,

435
00:22:27,911 --> 00:22:30,826
ukabona umujyanama muby'amategeko
ufite uburambe mubintu by'ibinyabuzima,

436
00:22:31,352 --> 00:22:34,821
urabizi ko.. yego uwo muntu afite uburambe
mubijyanye na za kampani zitangira,

437
00:22:34,821 --> 00:22:36,364
ariko atari mugice uri gukoreramo,

438
00:22:36,364 --> 00:22:38,554
kandi bishobora no kuba ari ibintu byihariye
mugice runaka

439
00:22:38,554 --> 00:22:39,826
ukeneye kumenyaho.

440
00:22:39,826 --> 00:22:42,161
Rero byaba ari byiza cyane uramutse ubonye
ufite uburambe

441
00:22:42,161 --> 00:22:44,257
mujyanye n'ibyo uri gukora.

442
00:22:45,649 --> 00:22:47,928
uwo muntu yijyeze aburanira
kampani zijyitangira?

443
00:22:47,928 --> 00:22:49,633
Ese yari afite ibibazo muminsi yashize?

444
00:22:49,633 --> 00:22:52,118
Uyu umnut yijyeze ahagararira
kampani zigitangira muminsi yashize,

445
00:22:52,118 --> 00:22:54,113
cyangwa yarazihuze arijyendera?

446
00:22:54,253 --> 00:22:56,374
rero ukeneye ko kumenya neza

447
00:22:56,563 --> 00:23:01,582
umujyanama muby'amategeko
afite uburambe,

448
00:23:01,718 --> 00:23:06,162
akorana kandi akagumana
nama kampani agitangira,

449
00:23:06,436 --> 00:23:08,310
munzira yose mubihe bitandukanye.

450
00:23:09,674 --> 00:23:12,354
Uyu muntu yijyeze yakora,
mubiganiro byo gushaka amafaranga?

451
00:23:12,354 --> 00:23:16,381
Kuko ni byiza cyane
iyo umunyamategeko wawe yumva neza

452
00:23:16,381 --> 00:23:18,868
uburyo bwo gushaka amafaranga wenda kujya ukoresha,

453
00:23:18,868 --> 00:23:20,221
cyangwa uteganya kubona

454
00:23:20,221 --> 00:23:22,221
ndetse akaba yagufasha ibiganiro

455
00:23:22,225 --> 00:23:24,998
kuko hari ibintu byinshi
bisa n'ibigoranye kumva mumategeko,

456
00:23:25,113 --> 00:23:26,917
Hari ibintu bigorana mumisoro,

457
00:23:26,918 --> 00:23:29,631
ingaruka z'imisoro kumyanzuro ufata
mumizo ya mbere,

458
00:23:29,774 --> 00:23:32,934
kandi ni byiza iyo uyu muntu
yakoze

459
00:23:32,973 --> 00:23:35,217
kubintu by'ibiganiro byo gushaka amafaranga,

460
00:23:35,217 --> 00:23:38,742
bijya gusa n'ibyo utekereza ko uzakora.

461
00:23:39,197 --> 00:23:41,954
kandi ibi bintu bibiri byanyuma
ari bintu by'umuntu kugiti cye,

462
00:23:41,954 --> 00:23:44,205
ariko se ufite umuntu warangiwe
n'umuntu mwakoranye wizeye?

463
00:23:44,365 --> 00:23:46,569
Uhawe amahitamo hagati y'aba banyamategeko babiri,

464
00:23:46,569 --> 00:23:49,801
umwe muri bo wamurangiwe n'incuti,

465
00:23:49,801 --> 00:23:51,757
cyangwa n'umuntu wakoze mubyo nawe uri gukoramo

466
00:23:51,757 --> 00:23:52,963
kandi wiyiziye neza,

467
00:23:52,963 --> 00:23:54,832
ndetse n'undi utaziho
icyintu na kimwe,

468
00:23:54,832 --> 00:23:57,514
hanyuma n'ubwo uwo muntu yaba
asa n'aho ahenze,

469
00:23:57,514 --> 00:24:00,368
byaba byumvikana neza
kujyana n'uwo bakurangiye.

470
00:24:00,368 --> 00:24:03,151
Hanyuma kandi, uwo muntu mujya imbizi?

471
00:24:03,151 --> 00:24:06,489
Muyandi magambo, murumvikana
n'uwo muntu, ese ushobora kumwizera,

472
00:24:06,489 --> 00:24:09,345
ese wabwira amabanga uwo mufasha muby'amategeko,

473
00:24:09,345 --> 00:24:12,629
kandi ashobora kukubwira ibintu by'ukuri
nawe ukamubwira uko wumva ibintu by'ukuri.

474
00:24:12,629 --> 00:24:14,661
icyo rero ni cyo gice
cy'ingenzi cyane muri ibi.

475
00:24:15,207 --> 00:24:18,192
Ni ibyo rero ib'ijyanye n'amategeko.

476
00:24:18,693 --> 00:24:22,863
nizere kandi ko 
ntabateye ubwoba cyane mbabwira

477
00:24:22,863 --> 00:24:24,752
ibibazo byose mushobora guhura nabyo;

478
00:24:24,752 --> 00:24:27,021
Ariko ndacyeka ko, muri rusange
kuri kampani zigitangira,

479
00:24:27,021 --> 00:24:30,813
Ni byiza gusobanukirwa
ibibazo ushobora kuba wahura nabyo hakiri kare,

480
00:24:30,813 --> 00:24:32,950
hanyuma ukagerageza uburyo
ushobora guhangana nabyo,

481
00:24:32,950 --> 00:24:37,583
aho kugirango utungurwe
n'ibibazo waratangiye gukora.

482
00:24:38,646 --> 00:24:41,138
Rero ndizera ko ibi bibajyirira akamaro
kandi mugumane natwe,

483
00:24:41,486 --> 00:24:44,598
Ni tugaruka ubukurikiyeho
tuzavuga kukwaguka.
